      <akn:section eId="sec_10_1202_08b">
        <akn:num>10-1202.08b</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Sports and Entertainment Fund.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_10-1202_08b_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>There is established as a nonlapsing fund the Sports and Entertainment Fund, to be maintained by the Authority.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_10-1202_08b_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_10-1202_08b_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Monies in the Sports and Entertainment Fund shall be used to pay for the operating expenses of the Authority, including expenses incurred through contracts, and for the hosting of sports events, sports teams, recreational events, and entertainment events in the District.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
